          <head type="stepTitle" xml:lang="en">Data analysis: How to use the generated 3D model for
            study the site</head>
          <desc type="definition" xml:lang="en"><p>In this step it is possible to perform the
              desired analysis, depending on the aim of the research to carry out. This is an
              illustrative and not limiting list of the possible analysis to perform: <list>
                <item>Cloud to Cloud (C2C) comparison</item>
                <item>Radiometric analysis (color change of the surfaces)</item>
                <item>DSM for surface comparison</item>
                <item>Soil volume excavated</item>
                <item>Visual interpretation</item>
                <item>GCP e CP analysis</item>
              </list>
            </p>
            <p> Software to use: <list>
                <item>Cloud Compare</item>
                <item>3D Reshaper</item>
              </list>
            </p>
          </desc>
